流程
1.安装nginx
mariadb-server mariadb-devel php php-fpm php-mysql

2.启动服务
nginx
systemctl start mariadb
systemctl start php-fpm

3.修改配置nginx.conf
location /{}
location ~ \.php${}


 location  ~  \.php$  {
            root           html;
            fastcgi_pass   127.0.0.1:9000;    #将请求转发给本机9000端口，PHP解释器
            fastcgi_index  index.php;
            #fastcgi_param   SCRIPT_FILENAME  $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;
            include        fastcgi.conf;
        }
[root@proxy ~]# vim /usr/local/nginx/html/test1.php
<?php
$i="This is a test Page";
echo $i;
?>

用户----nginx----php(脚本---数据库)

https

gcc openssl-devel pcre-devel


PHP-FPM(FastCGI Process Manager：FastCGI进程管理器)
php php的脚本解释器

地址重写
rewirte 旧地址(支持正则) 新地址 [选项]
rewirte /a.html /b.html ;
rewrite ^/(.*)      https://www.baidu.com/$1; redirect 
条件重写

#注意 if 后面必须有空格
if ($http_user_agent ~* chrome){
    rewrite ^/(.*) https://www.baidu.com/$1
    }
    
